{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "e6e2e83d-c5bd-4199-b819-655cc0f4de22", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e6e2e83d-c5bd-4199-b819-655cc0f4de22@1.pkg/1772597690553/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597691002", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e6e2e83d-c5bd-4199-b819-655cc0f4de22@1.pkg/1772597690553/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597691002"}, "identifier": "e6e2e83d-c5bd-4199-b819-655cc0f4de22", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查 &ldquo;探问人生目标&rdquo; 的知识。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③</span><span>：李大钊的话强调人生目标对前行的指引作用，启示我们要主动规划人生、确立目标，让其成为成长指引，符合 &ldquo;探问人生目标&rdquo; 中目标对人生的导向价值，故</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③</span><span>正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>：&ldquo;目标越宏大越有价值&rdquo; 错误，有意义的人生目标应契合自身与社会需求，并非单纯看是否宏大；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>：&ldquo;目标既定就需一成不变&rdquo; 错误，人生充满变化，可依据实际灵活调整目标，这是合理规划人生的体现；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>答案选 B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">李大钊曾以航海为喻，寄语青年 &ldquo;临开始活动以前，应该定定方向。譬如航海远行的人，必先定个目的地，中途指针总指向它，才有望抵达；若方向不定，随风飘转，恐永难到达&rdquo; 。这启示我们（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①人生目标是推动前行的 &ldquo;指南针&rdquo;，能指引成长方向</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②青年要尽早确立人生目标，且目标越宏大越有价值</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③应主动规划人生，让目标成为奋斗的稳定指引</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④目标既定就需一成不变，方能抵达 &ldquo;目的地&rdquo;</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）李大钊曾以航海为喻，寄语青年 “临开始活动以前，应该定定方向。譬如航海远行的人，必先定个目的地，中途指针总指向它，才有望抵达；若方向不定，随风飘转，恐永难到达” 。这启示我们（ ）①人生目标是推动前行的 “指南针”，能指引成长方向②青年要尽早确立人生目标，且目标越宏大越有价值③应主动规划人生，让目标成为奋斗的稳定指引④目标既定就需一成不变，方能抵达 “目的地”", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e6e2e83d-c5bd-4199-b819-655cc0f4de22@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984659457", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②④</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③④</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">李大钊曾以航海为喻，寄语青年 &ldquo;临开始活动以前，应该定定方向。譬如航海远行的人，必先定个目的地，中途指针总指向它，才有望抵达；若方向不定，随风飘转，恐永难到达&rdquo; 。这启示我们（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①人生目标是推动前行的 &ldquo;指南针&rdquo;，能指引成长方向</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②青年要尽早确立人生目标，且目标越宏大越有价值</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③应主动规划人生，让目标成为奋斗的稳定指引</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④目标既定就需一成不变，方能抵达 &ldquo;目的地&rdquo;</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878